item.title: Test Blog
item.description:
Hello World! This is my portoflio and blog site.

And before you ask.. My username is Agent Galahad (agntgalahad) from one of the best spy movie series ‘The Kingsman’ (we dont count the last movie)

I’m a Computer Science student with a big passion for robotics, machine learning, and computer vision. Right now, I’m at IIT Bombay working computer vision algorithms and drones.

I’m gearing up for an MS in Robotics soon, but for now, this site is where I share my projects, ideas, and whatever else I’m building.
